{"tid":2030694,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"其實中共強行推23條對佢哋有利","createTime":"2020-05-23T02:44:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-23T02:49:52.000Z","uid":250273,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8c7e67cd7eacc5c4b198f60bb4eed8bae915cc62","tid":2030694,"uid":250273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T02:44:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">外資撤走</span><br />\n當外國企業離開香港，資金流走，中共就可以派更多<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">中資</span></span>落嚟香港，然後控制本地經濟市場<br />\n呢個方法對佢哋有咩好處？就係會打底<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">黃色經濟圈</span></span>，令到黃店唔敢再出現對抗佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />意味香港人以後食<span style=\"color: blue;\">金拱門，敏華，美心集團</span>等<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為當中共派大量中資入咗黎香港嘅經濟市場，佢哋會可以大量<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">開藍店</span></span>，叫香港人不斷俾錢佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <br />\n中資繼續入侵本地經濟市場，仲可以去搞地產界，<br />\n提高本港樓價，令到<span style=\"color: gold;\">香港人</span>繼續買唔到樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">中共強行推23條，唔單止係實現攬炒，更加想要控制香港經濟市場，因為一單成功控制嘅話，香港人就要聽佢哋話事，繼續幫佢哋搵錢。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">所以香港人，我地真係唔輸得㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>一定要對抗到底</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">524,527見</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"117f80f80586b49a8a6e1a9ef7537ee594bc8ae5","tid":2030694,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T02:45:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"924656fb3fd10ea8a97a7c29729b68625280c1e4","tid":2030694,"uid":39200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T02:45:59.000Z","msg":"為左打殘黃色經濟圈而唔要美金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e407c64dc212a6031f7ff02ed885727dda1b57e","tid":2030694,"uid":250273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T02:46:15.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af48901cdba5df3cd3ac597663ec83dab9347d43","tid":2030694,"uid":355289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T02:47:28.000Z","msg":"賺唔到外資嘅香港有咩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ce077cea36ba3ba0ac1e78ea92a8d4483b6bba8","tid":2030694,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T02:47:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />. <br />\n會提名樓主達爾文獎"},{"pid":"54627c4263b722df651ce57bd5145855accf080d","tid":2030694,"uid":250273,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"924656fb3fd10ea8a97a7c29729b68625280c1e4","tid":2030694,"uid":39200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T02:45:59.000Z","msg":"為左打殘黃色經濟圈而唔要美金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T02:48:20.000Z","msg":"係控制本地經濟市場，要香港人<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">俾錢食藍店</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06dc283c5f1d5cc0a199d4d3e2a471115c4ea7df","tid":2030694,"uid":45708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"